'''Bal'ta'ran crystals''' were [[Mineral/Legends|mineral]] formations on [[Guiteica/Legends|Guiteica]].<ref name="a">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

[[Planet/Legends|Planet]] Guiteica held extensive underground reserves of this mineral. [[Slavery/Legends|Slave]]-operated [[Mining/Legends|mines]] on [[Upper Bal'ta'ran Cluster]] obtained these [[Crystal/Legends|crystals]]. Many different pro-[[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] mining companies had tried to convince native [[Bitthævrian/Legends|Bitthævrians]] to perform mining activity on the planet.<ref name="a" />

